Class VoiceConsoleCommandExtensionTest

  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    InterpretCommandTest, SayCommandTest, VoicesCommandTest
    public abstract class VoiceConsoleCommandExtensionTest
extends JavaOSGiTest
    A base class for the classes testing the different commands of the VoiceConsoleCommandExtension. It takes care of the mocks, stubs and services that are used in all the extending classes.
    Author:
    Mihaela Memova - Initial contribution, Velin Yordanov - migrated tests from groovy to java
